title: Tales of Xillia - A Swimsuit 3 Years Later and Best Lingerie 2 Years Later (Doujinshi)
description:
- A Swimsuit 3 Years Later and Best Lingerie 2 Years Later
3 years later, Elise is around 15. Together only with Alvin, they go to the beach. Alvin's in for a (n obvious) surprise: She's wearing a swimsuit. He makes a promise... 

- Then...
The sequel to Swimsuits & Lingerie. The promised day of 3 years later has come. Alvin and Elise share a tender moment together after their wedding ceremony, conveying how much they love one another.
